ASHESI UNIVERSITY
EXPENTIAL TRANSCRIPT

The Ashesi Experiential Transcript captures students’ endeavours in ways that demonstrate
their assimilation of the values of Ashesi University: Scholarship, Leadership and Citizenship.
Ashesi University validates all information presented on a student’s Ashesi Experiential
Transcript. Each record in this transcript is verified and evaluated using the standard of the
university’s core values.
